{"tid":1827432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post求推上熱門] 場運動唔係淡左 而係要重燃抗爭氣氛","createTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T19:17:40.000Z","uid":265917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a63f441105c28d5cfad165ba55460f76600d07d","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想多啲人參與行動？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要記住嚟場革命唔係淨係屬於後生仔<br />\n四五十歲既人多數淨係上fb 佢地好多時都想參與行動 但又唔知有咩日程</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地有咩可以做？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1）我地要多啲<span style=\"color: red;\">係fb唔同post下面瘋狂洗版行動文宣</span><br />\n2）仲有要<span style=\"color: red;\">係街不斷airdrop啲文宣</span>俾人製造抗爭氣氛<br />\n3）隨身袋住啲文宣周街貼</strong></span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好淨係依賴文宣組<br />\n頭兩項都係零成本 <br />\n你唔係唔做呀嘛</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XjgKx0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XjgKx0.png&h=6d4c2a1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PNPP4x1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPNPP4x1.jpg&h=121f751a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWnE6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWnE6n.jpg&h=8c4e5bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我諗大家有時都會見到我洗版 但會付諸行動既唔知幾多個<br />\n我講既野係老生常談 但就係越簡單既嘢越少人做</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想係度宣傳下<br />\n<br />\n有個音樂天才既手足好癲 <br />\n自己拍左個&lt;願榮光歸香港&gt;既one man band version<br />\n<br />\n手足一個人演奏曬小提琴 中提琴 大提琴 低音大提琴 鋼琴 長笛 高中低音笛 巴松管<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以㩒入去睇下條片 <br />\n支持下手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TVXGhxDC9UY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTVXGhxDC9UY&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a9cac6f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TVXGhxDC9UY</a>"},{"pid":"156c15f4b504afce2cb80c0c91965d866d53d8c7","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9708b23f812d4c11f02212b6c072b530e7e6e9e0","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996b77c8f5589024810a5ecbbe57c841d870200b","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135cd6b04f419579e928c3b5f2fac160c45acace","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bba50c09ee20c7d3fafd852556fed8e91520fb8","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a782226e801d1c987bda8f10daf414879227c97c","tid":1827432,"uid":265917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img